Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:07.98,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本片輕描淡寫地講述了南家三姐妹平凡的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:10.35,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要過度期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5  6  7  8  9…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪  保阪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝天椒要切成絲放進去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多炒會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了  速水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪你想繼續做料理到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多此一問
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人只要活著就少不了吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不做料理之日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是死亡之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是可以考慮偶爾用些其它方法來引春香注意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方說  你看  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10  11  12  13  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14  15  16  17…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是16
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於這個越來越冷的季節是必不可少的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始努力說不定能趕在耶誕節之前送出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提從今年的流行和我的喜好上來說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推薦這種感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  加油試試看吧  保阪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寒假到來之前完成它…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了南春香開始做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術上的確進步了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還沒有讓她笑過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前連話都沒有說過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不成熟的雙手不論做什麼都不成的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來我令南春香展開笑容的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時再開始織東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓她和女兒們得到溫暖的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香說過喜歡織的東西喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼從今天開始我也喜歡織東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,31  誒？  我說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,32  33  34  35  36  37…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在編織的時候最重要的是平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦躁了會織錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力過大會網眼會纏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適當休息下  做些伸展運動之類的悠閒地織吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之享受才是織東西的精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？網眼多了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:03:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個網眼用力不均寬度就會變嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真深奧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,55  56  57  58…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的聖誕節可以期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:42.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,310)}聖夜、神仙下凡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希穿了新大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:04:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為變冷了  不過今天更冷了一個級別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  特別冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子的圍巾毛絨絨的感覺很厚很暖和  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個很暖和所以很中意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希的大衣感覺也很暖和真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是新買的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就買了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很適合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希問問題的意圖很容易懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子能理解我問題的意圖真是幫了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有點煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子  想問你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡味的牛奶可哥和加了過多的乳脂的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個更好些？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得哪個更好些？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可哥？咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為選哪個而煩惱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在打比方？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡味牛奶可哥和放了過多的乳脂的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道淡加點就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一邊只要再加些咖啡就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還要加熱水和糖…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把放多了的味道調回去會很難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得可哥更好些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然嗎  淳子也這樣想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真希今天早上穿的大衣是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「淡味的牛奶可哥」色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選哪個都是不對的麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了保阪學長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子  你怎樣想？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個到底是重複了呢還是沒重複呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白意圖的二選一問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會不會選哪個都是不對的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個重複了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有重複嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能兩個都不是呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得真希新大衣的顏色和南春香大衣的顏色重複了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本身並不是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上說答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是少見的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複了也正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拿鐵咖啡的顏色進入到視線的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會困惑也是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無處可去的心情該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無計可施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為什麼  無處可去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些問題似乎多想無用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛進行時裡說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生的價值是由被男生告白的次數決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說那句話的是競爭對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在那之後被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管這樣我覺得還是有一番道理的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何內田  最近很受歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:43.07,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想也無濟於事的話還是不要去想了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒受歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我怎樣才能受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  淳子  老實說你很受歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？果然很受歡迎嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是有受歡迎秘訣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣才能受歡迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣才能受歡迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我什麼都沒有想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂內田  什麼都不想就會受歡迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？夏奈那種事情可能嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你們在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來淳子是被稱為魔女的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定擁有魔法之類的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的魔法使？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一個說害羞的話也不臉紅的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那種事情  淳子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我受歡迎的秘訣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我戀愛的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上皇家奶茶色的大衣之類的會好一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  有皇家奶茶色的大衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  借我皇家奶茶色的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:56.92,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我什麼腦筋都沒動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不借
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:00.60,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  好嘛拜託了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有給你用的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼啊千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上了春香的皇家奶茶色的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就受歡迎了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把別人認成了南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空也在嘲笑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到下的這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂純白就是那樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  掀開窗簾就是滿面的銀色世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我醒來的時候窗簾已經被妹妹拉開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經相當的興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跳出窗外被雪埋上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妹妹已經這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我也像她那麼年輕也會跳出去被雪埋上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話真想雪再積得深一些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就可以堆雪屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫馨的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會下雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36.8度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低燒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美  哪裡不舒服麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些乏力  量了體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只是低燒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香學姐也來量體溫？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些乏力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然變冷了  很怕感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上的雪也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我先離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在走廊上幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…還是扣上比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才量體溫之後忘記扣上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你看到了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用這種堅定又純真的少年的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮  簡直就是滿面的純白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別特地把顏色說出來啊  純白什麼的別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為打開著一下子就充滿了視野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是故意的…什麼  興…興奮？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來軟綿綿地非常柔軟  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛撲上去一定很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛…飛撲什麼的  就在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危險  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是再年輕一些就會撲上去深埋進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是有多大啊  不是跟我同歲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來還真可惜  能再大一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你也看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36.5也算正常體溫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還是有些乏力  不過加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我說  夏樹看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了…還是說快要看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是白茫茫的一片呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的純白色了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點也沒在看！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明積了這麼多雪  是沒在看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美  在生什麼氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為別的  都是因為夏樹那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個差勁的男人  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不揍他一頓就咽不下這口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口被那傢伙看了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是目不轉睛的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…剛才…夏樹他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還用少年純真的眼神說什麼純白很漂亮什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純白？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說他很興奮什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興奮…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說看起來軟綿綿很柔軟的樣子  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想飛撲上去什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想飛撲上去？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還說要是再年輕一些就危險了什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說我已經老了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還說要是再大一點就好了  太差勁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
